beer.beer_description:
The Rye Hard IPA is burnt orange in colour with a lacy, creamy head. The aroma is a blend of floral, herbal and citrus notes with a spicy, fruity finish from the addition of Bramling Cross and Santiam hops.

This IPA features eight unique hops and its full, malty flavour has hints of orange, mandarin and an earthy hop bitterness, which finishes dry and spicy from the addition of rye.
